OL,3,C2.2 overdoses per day in south of
OL,4,CScotland- with figures climbing in 2024
OL,6,FEvery day, of every month, for the
OL,7,Fpast three years, an ambulance has
OL,8,Fbeen dispatched somewhere in largely
OL,9,Frural southern Scotland to deal with a
OL,10,Fsuspected overdose.
OL,12,FExclusive data obtained by ITV News
OL,13,FBorder showed that there were an
OL,14,Faverage of 2.2 ambulance call-outs to
OL,15,Fa suspected overdose across Dumfries
OL,16,Fand Galloway and the Scottish Borders
OL,17,Fin 2023, with a total of 821 recorded
OL,18,Fduring the year.
