OL,6,FHowever figures have dropped slightly
OL,7,Fsince 2021, when the data showed an
OL,8,Faverage of 2.4 incidents a day were
OL,9,Frecorded.
OL,11,FData was obtained via a Freedom of
OL,12,FInformation request to the Scottish
OL,13,FAmbulance Service, and isn't broken
OL,14,Fdown by type of overdose - so could
OL,15,Finclude those caused by alcohol and
OL,16,Fother legal substances. It also
OL,17,Fdoesn't differentiate between
OL,18,Fdeliberate and accidental overdoses.
