OL,6,FScott Richardson, a harm reduction
OL,7,Fworker for the drug and alcohol
OL,8,Fcharity With You in the border's town
OL,9,Fof Galashiels, said he wasn't
OL,10,Fsurprised by the numbers.
OL,12,F"There is a lot of people out there
OL,13,Fwho are having some challenges with
OL,14,Fsubstance misuse at the moment," he
OL,15,Fsaid.
