OL,6,FHe suggested that poly-drug use, where
OL,7,Fpeople use more than one substance at
OL,8,Fthe same time, was contributing to the
OL,9,Fnumbers. There are also concerns that
OL,10,Fpowerful nitazene type drugs are
OL,11,Fentering the supply, increasing the
OL,12,Frisks of overdose.
OL,14,F"It's the strength, the potency of
OL,15,Fit," Scott explained. "It's a lot more
OL,16,Fstronger than heroin."
