OL,6,FScotland remains the drug deaths
OL,7,Fcapital of Europe, recording 1,172
OL,8,Fdeaths in 2023. One former addict who
OL,9,Fnow volunteers for support service
OL,10,FBorders in Recovery told ITV News he
OL,11,Fhad suffered from multiple overdoses.
OL,13,F"My go to substances were the ones
OL,14,Fthat numbed me the most," Scott Happer
OL,15,Fsaid. "Heroin, benzodiazepines, which,
OL,16,Ftaken together, can be really
OL,17,Fdangerous."
OL,19,F"I'm lucky to be here really," he
OL,20,Fadded.
