OL,6,FIn a statement the Scottish Health
OL,7,FSecretary Neil Gray said: "Increasing
OL,8,Fthe provision and availability of
OL,9,Fnaloxone, which provides time for
OL,10,Femergency services to arrive and for
OL,11,Ffurther treatment to be given, is a
OL,12,Fkey priority in our national mission
OL,13,Fto reduce harm and help save lives.
OL,15,F"Figures show 7,589 take home naloxone
OL,16,Fkits were issued from October to
OL,17,FDecember last year for those at risk
OL,18,Fof opioid overdose.
